{"tid":1711252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣收班狗皮（內附效果圖）","createTime":"2019-11-12T10:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T11:37:32.000Z","uid":304589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7639cb3f995e0730cd94fafc989e6a96f7ccc83f","tid":1711252,"uid":304589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"大家以前有冇烚過d潺弱同學?點解烚得咁過癮，就係知道個同學廢，冇還撃之力。到有一日個同學同你死過，你就唔會敢烚佢。<br />\n<br />\n點解班狗殺到咁撚high?如果你知道殺人強姦無法律後果，對家又無力還擊，講真係你，都可能同佢地一樣<br />\n<br />\n要班狗驚，要班狗收歛，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武力一定要升級</span></span></strong>。唔好覺得無驚無險又有糧岀，隨時有錢冇命享。及早回頭是岸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我打機過陣仲有兩樣唔駛埋身的武器，強酸彈，效果類似以下新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/posts/2926206114087408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FSaluteToHKPolice%2Fposts%2F2926206114087408&d=9CaroZtPfqcCLVRp0XVEkXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=e772ad51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/SaluteToHKPolice/posts/2926206114087408</a><br />\n（效果圖）<br />\n<br />\n仲有用叉差撘波子，千祈要射準d，射腳就好，唔好射錯人，唔好射頭，射頭真係會爆。我聽以前啲ching講，攞黎射雀係可以打穿隻雀仔！<br />\n<br />\n另，唔好再講咩禍不及妻兒<br />\n<br />\n係，好唔人道，但有人對住學生隻眼，心口開槍，佢地又有當過學生係人咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有殺人犯填命，我地成立慶祝日，每年到果日，全民上街慶祝！<br />\n<br />\n武裝起來，fright for freedom!"},{"pid":"c82aa6188d2dc04681fa87ec8685a761872e2f43","tid":1711252,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:46:07.000Z","msg":"⚠轉出去⚠<br />\n❗大學 Lab 善用化學品反抗❗<br />\n❗HNO3❗<br />\n❗Mg❗<br />\n❗NH4NO3❗<br />\n❗NaOH❗<br />\n❗ANFO❗<br />\n❗ANSU❗<br />\n❗H2SO4❗"},{"pid":"1dd10695c757d51f9f3fbbdd2324db3b04115f26","tid":1711252,"uid":304589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"P牌照推"},{"pid":"dc29b73b53f3381df55828c09805cd204e21e312","tid":1711252,"uid":304589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:48:48.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"